## 🏗️ Pipeline Architecture

```
 Input Document (PDF / Image / Scan)
          │
          ▼
┌─────────────────────┐
│  Pre-processing      │   • Image denoising, deskewing
│  (OpenCV)           │   • Resolution enhancement
└──────────┬──────────┘   • File format normalization
           │
           ▼
┌─────────────────────┐
│  OCR Engine         │   • Tesseract OCR (primary)
│  (Tesseract /       │   • AWS Textract (fallback for low quality)
│   AWS Textract)     │   • Confidence scoring per token
└──────────┬──────────┘
           │
           ▼
┌─────────────────────┐
│  NER Extraction     │   • Custom BERT fine-tuned on KYC docs
│  (BERT + spaCy)     │   • Extracts: Name, DOB, ID Numbers,
│                     │     Address, PAN, Aadhaar patterns
└──────────┬──────────┘
           │
           ▼
┌─────────────────────┐
│  Fraud Scoring      │   • XGBoost anomaly scorer
│  (XGBoost)          │   • Checks: tamper detection, font
│                     │     inconsistency, duplicate submission
└──────────┬──────────┘
           │
           ▼
┌─────────────────────┐
│  Verification &     │   • Cross-field validation rules
│  Output             │   • Confidence threshold gating
│                     │   • Auto-approve / flag for review
└─────────────────────┘
```

