## 🚀 Key Features

### 1. Self-Learning Feedback Loop
Human corrections on low-confidence extractions automatically feed into weekly model retraining — improving accuracy from **91% at launch to 99.1% over 6 months**.

### 2. Serverless at Scale
Deployed on **AWS Lambda** with auto-scaling — processes 200K+ documents/month at peak, maintaining 99.95% uptime at just **$0.002 per document**.

### 3. Multi-Engine OCR
Primary Tesseract OCR with automatic fallback to AWS Textract for low-quality scans, with per-token confidence scoring to maximize extraction accuracy.

### 4. Airflow Orchestration
Full pipeline observability with Airflow DAGs — retry logic, alerting, SLA monitoring, and audit trails for compliance requirements.

